Jeff and Mackenzie Bezos Jeff Bezos and his wife, MacKenzie are officially divorced, after 25 years of marriage. The duo’s divorce was finalised on Friday after a King County, Washington judge signed an order formalizing the separation. According to Bloomberg, MacKenzie will be taking 4% of  Amazon’s holding, which is valued at $38.3 billion. MacKenzie Bezos becomes the 20th wealthiest billionaire on the 2019 Forbes Rich List, ahead of Telsa’s Elon Musk and Alibaba founder Jack Ma. Jeff Bezos, still retains a 12% stake worth $114.8 billion and remains the world’s wealthiest person. The post Judge signs Order Formalising Jeff Bezos & Mackenzie Bezos’ Divorce appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija